&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt;Modality LLP is a large-scale provider on NHS community outpatient and diagnostic services. Locally, we offer patients access to community outpatient services across a number of specialty areas including Cardiology, Dermatology, Rheumatology, Pain Management, ENT, Gynaecology, Ophthalmology, Orthopaedics, Paediatrics, Urology and Respiratory Medicine. We also offer a range of diagnostic services including x-ray and ultrasound.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt;As we continue to expand, we are looking to recruit to a new vacancy, Head of Imaging, who will provide clinical leadership to Modality’s Imaging services including plain film x-ray and ultrasound and lead the development of new imaging services including MRI and CT. The postholder will oversee the operational management of Imaging services on a day-to-day basis by line managing clinical staff and planning effective service delivery.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;We are able to accommodate flexible working including full and part time roles&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt;If you would like an informal discussion about the role please email aamena.salar@nhs.net or sapna.shannon@nhs.net &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;em&gt;The closing date for applications will be &lt;/em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Friday 6th November&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
